    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey @harshmaur following this I am wondering if a good solution for you right now could be to use VirtualRefinements so that your refinements are always applied even when unmounted.\n\nBasically not only you have to use rendering refinements but also also have virtual refinements mounted so their state is always applied.\n\nThis should work. Let me know.\n",
